# devices/turing-rk1 -- board-specific kernel config (curated slice).
# The RK1's board delta is expressed in its device tree, not in kconfig, so no
# board-only CONFIG symbols are required beyond soc/rk3588 + accel/full. Kept as an
# explicit (empty) slice so the device layer's `device_config_fragments` has a stable
# target, and so a second RK3588 board can add its board-only symbols here.
